[32m+[m[32m  notes;[m
[32m+[m[32m}[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Confidence[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mConfidence is advisory and should be normalized to `0-100`.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mSuggested interpretation:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- `90-100`: authoritative-looking source, human-confirmed, or field-confirmed.[m
[32m+[m[32m- `70-89`: strong source but not human-certified.[m
[32m+[m[32m- `40-69`: useful source with incomplete metadata.[m
[32m+[m[32m- `1-39`: weak match, inferred, stale, or conflicting.[m
[32m+[m[32m- `0`: unknown, failed, or not applicable.[m
[32m+[m
