[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIf two evidence records disagree:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Preserve both evidence records.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Do not silently replace either.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Attach conflict notes.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Require human review before promotion into ScopeVersion truth.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Human Override[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mHuman override creates evidence.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mHuman override evidence should include:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- reviewer identity when available.[m
[32m+[m[32m- timestamp.[m
[32m+[m[32m- reason.[m
[32m+[m[32m- prior evidence references.[m
[32m+[m[32m- changed normalized value.[m
